manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Winsome Shaye Dining Table Style and integrity of construction define the Winsome Wood Shaye Oblong Dining Table. The tabletop has a softly curved profile that adds refinement to the design. The solid, tapered legs have a distinctive notch where they meet the frame that give it a unique, contemporary look. Simple yet attractive and versatile for its oblong shape and size. A suitable table for a breakfast nook, for a studio apartment, or comfortably sits a family of four in the dining room. This Shaye table will combine great with several of the Winsome Wood dining chairs (each sold separately). Generous height clearance from floor to aprons at 25.59”H, that allows for dining chairs of any style. Made of remarkably sturdy solid wood in a warm walnut finish, this handsome piece will mesh beautifully with just about any decor. Specifications Overall dims 47.24"W x 29.53"D x 29.13"H Inside dims between legs of widest side 39.72"W x 25.59"H Inside dims between legs of shortest side 24.13"W x 25.59"H Features Constructed of Solid Wood Tabletop has softly curved profile Ships in 1 box Assembly Required

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Gorgeous and solid for the price!
reviews.reviewText: I couldn't believe the price for this solid walnut table! I bought it to go with my Christopher Knight chairs and you'd never know they didn't come together! The assembly couldn't be easier, 2 screws per leg and it sits solidly!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Using this as a computer desk
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a bigger computer desk to fit 2 monitors with a 30 inch depth at least. Most of the typical computer desk are 24 inch in depth and I don't want to sit to close to my monitors.I found this table on sale that fits my needs. It is easy to assemble. Definitely sturdy enough for 2 monitors and more.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 30, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Very nice table. Sturdy, well-made. Solid wood. I do not regret buying this. Thank you seller!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2021
reviews.reviewText: As pictured. I waited until the price was right and feel it was a great value. The table is solid and smooth and a good size for four to sit comfortably.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My home office table
reviews.reviewText: I love this table. Easy to assemble and seems very sturdy. I use it for my home office and it works great.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Made from very small pieces of wood.
reviews.reviewText: The table looks decent but it’s not good quality. It’s made out of very small (8”x3” ish) pieces of wood and you can see the zig zag cross sections throughout the top as pictured. For the price, it’ll do for now though until I find a nicer option.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 14, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Smaller than I imagined but beautiful
reviews.reviewText: I think this table is beautiful, though it is a bit smaller than I had imagined it to be. It is perfect as a large desk, or a dining table for a small family, but you can't really have more than 4 people at it. It is very pretty and feels sturdy

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 30, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Feels like a quality table, but you can’t use it if it doesn’t come with all the legs
reviews.reviewText: Arrived today, and was super excited to put it together. Sadly, I opened the box and it was only a table top, two legs and instructions. Table top feels solid so that’s a good thing. I followed the instructions for replacement parts, and sent the manufacturer an email. Hoping I get them sooner or later. I work in furniture so I know how the industry is about sending out parts. Hoping for the best. Will update when item is put together.Update as of 5/13: Replacement parts arrive from the vendor after 2 weeks. Table was easy to put together. Table is solid and quite heavy. It is definitely more red than I had hoped. I like the style just wish it was more of a true dark walnut color

Very happy with this table, NO veneer, solid wood throughout. Easy 15 min assembly, just LOOSELY bolt all 4 legs on first, THEN tighten the bolts. Lock-washers are included, so no need to over-tighten the bolts, the lock-washers will keep them tight, just tighten snuggly, then stop! This way you don't strip the threads and end up with a loose leg. Very happy with this table, great quality at this price point. I would highly recommend!
I love the mid century modern style of this table! Its very small but is a perfect fit for my small basement suite. The only negative thing I would have to say is that it scratches really easily :(

reviews.reviewTitle: Nice minimalist design, great value for money
reviews.reviewText: I've seen this elsewhere for 50% more than what I paid on Amazon. That, combined with reasonable quality and great looks, means no regrets. Sure, the wood is soft, so will take a beating over the years, and is engineered, so not quite a hand-made presentation, but they have still done a terrific job!
